{"type": "article", "id": 25141, "title": "大象桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115107UifRcnwpMr5Xkou9.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把像大象一样的椅子来自法国设计师Marc Venot，从椅子背后看，环形靠背和椅腿连在一起构成了大象头的形状，简易而可爱。有趣的是它配上一个看起来很普通的方桌子后，就像在大象头后面加了一个大象的身体，拥有更强的趣味和互动。有棕色和蓝色两种选择，它目前已可以生产，<a href=\"http://eo.dk/elephant-chair-table/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115105cZ97rwX3HjlbNd41.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151055wdThqULzYxsjPHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115106opWeRTnx2DY4Fr16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115106wcCse0IEOQX4zuAF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115106yaC9UOZDXH4gx6Qw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}